---
title: Fig and Quinoa Salad with Arugula, Mint, and Feta
description: Calling this a “salad” doesn’t do it justice. From the protein- packed quinoa, fiber-rich figs, and heart-healthy arugula, this dish packs a serious nutritional (and flavor) punch. It’s one of our go-to vegetarian meals, and we’ve got a feeling you’ll love it just as much as we do.
